description:
Danny welcomes Emerson Collins (People's Couch, Rent Live!) to recap this week's Lohan Beach Club. Danny also tells the devastating tale of losing a choir solo in 8th grade, Emerson talks about getting catfished, they discuss Dina on Celebrity Big Brother, and more.


Emerson/Lohan Beach Recap: 8:58ish
